      public boolean addBranch(Branch branch)
      Adds input Branch object into the DataBase
      Parameters:
      branch - Branch object to be written/stored into the DataBase
      Returns:
    • Returns true if adding branch into DataBase was Successful
    • Returns False if Branch to be added already exists, hence nothing will be added into DataBase

    • removeBranch

      public Branch removeBranch(String branchName)
      Searches DataBase for requested Branch, removes the Branch from DataBase and returns removed Branch
      Parameters:
      branchName - String Name of the Branch to be removed
      Returns:
    • Returns Removed Branch object if removal from DataBase was successful
    • Returns False if Branch to be remove does not exist within DataBase, hence no removal is made.
